            <lg xml:id="TK640">
<l>muṟaippaṭac cūḻntu muṭivilavē ceyvar </l>
<l>tiṟappā ṭilāa tavar</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those ministers who are destitute of (executive) ability will fail to carry out their projects, although they may have contrived aright.</l>
